Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,木漏れ日みたいで、いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空 雲 果てしない道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっちゃい存在同士 手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと 壮大 夢見てもいいかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて 寛大な 地球だい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう、きっと特別な双眼鏡だって、ね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,探した景色は見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,世界で一番の絶景ポイントは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも目の前の「その笑顔」だったから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう いつもとなりにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけでもう何もいらなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なかなか素直に言えないこの気持ちあふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日もコハルビヨリだ いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一句「謝謝你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就像掠過樹梢的陽光 讚♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,藍天 白雲 漫漫長路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣渺小的存在 只要手牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就能心懷更壯大的夢想？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,地球多麼寬大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就算特製的望遠鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,也找不到心中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,因為世界上最棒的景點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就是時刻綻放在眼前的那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你陪伴我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,有你相伴 別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿心中的這份心情 總是說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是暖和的小陽春 讚♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:29.68,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}翻譯：dgwxx／其他：cunhan
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次谷川岳倒是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今後可就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山確實挺花錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去打工不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有時候也會打工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學家教？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 這樣分數的加法就好懂多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 日向老師好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是沒打過工 不會很累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實不輕鬆就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只要能賺錢 就能做很多事情了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用自己賺的錢買到防水衝鋒衣的時候好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在雨中到處跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨還到處跑啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工雖然不容易 但能累積經驗 一定會開闊視野的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小葵說不定做不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又想用激將法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太露骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 打工什麼的我也可以的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:54.15,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(954,718)\bord1}我要打工了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過打工可以 別耽誤學業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那想打什麼工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就開始找…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 媽媽的朋友在開西點麵包店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個商業街的會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 鈴叔之前說人手不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打電話去問問看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認識的人更放心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是雪村家的女兒 叫小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久疏問候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 小葵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 聽媽媽說您那正在找工讀生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道您願不願意僱用我 打電話問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵這麼可愛 當然歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 待會能過來嗎 兩點左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太突然了 不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係沒關係 當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘記帶履歷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,履歷！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姓名 地址 動機…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的字好難看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 還剩一小時了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！打工的參加動機怎麼寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的要打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就寫為愛好賺錢 不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要讓對方認為你會認真工作就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證件照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去拍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍的時候要微笑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過小葵可不怎麼會笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 面試的時候要微笑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,措辭也很重要 但第一印象靠表情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的笑容那麼陰暗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容 笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要上場了確實有難度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 按這個鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再拍一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！剛剛的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 好久不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說最近開始登山了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是健康的愛好 不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下有空？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去參加商業街聯會 店裡就剩一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在能去幫幫她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服在裡面的更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺寸不合適的話告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不明白的就問店裡的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 履歷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮是不是紮起來比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這打扮有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡有點慌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這個 和這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我之後會在這裡打工 我叫雪村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小野塚光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大學二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我小光喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你好可愛噢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好隨便的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次打工 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之客人一進來 就大聲問候「歡迎光臨」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後問客人想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重複一遍 收款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 教你怎麼用收銀機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好粗線條啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是坐辦公室的工作比較適合我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好悶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話的時候要用中氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 沒錯就是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要大聲問候喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不做也得做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡 歡迎光臨 您要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 是 要蘋果派和花飾蛋糕 還有芒果蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用著急 做事用心紮實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掃條碼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1,420日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收您2,000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找您580日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油噢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始很難為情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思直視對方的話 就看對方眼睛下方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之要面對客人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時加上微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你自己是客人的話 有店員的微笑接待一定很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是本店推薦噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎再來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光姐 本來以為是個隨隨便便的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作還真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好囉 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人們購物也都很舒適
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人看表情 表情改變印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 一定是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！我也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在呢在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 我可是客人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去你家晃晃 結果聽說你已經來面試了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這家店很好 我經常來買喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小葵還會擺臉色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也是在這裡打工的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫日向 小葵受您關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡 小葵幹得很好呢 很不錯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊！好意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說日向 別耽誤我做事了 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來的時候 笑容很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個臭日向 囉哩叭嗦的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 彷彿心裡輕鬆了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵今天很幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 第一份打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累趴了 不過累得舒服 很有成就感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 工作和登山很相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽不會是在這等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些擔心呢 在家等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了吧 回家吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次打工 不過幾個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我感到眼界開闊多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有些緊張 但心裡很期待明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待續
